{"tid":1096071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門醫院疑吸大麻醫生無條件獲釋","createTime":"2019-04-07T12:49:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T16:10:37.000Z","uid":11148,"like":22,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4899e26c6e13c9ae238ec7d8d3d345a205d746ae","tid":1096071,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:49:55.000Z","msg":"早前屯門醫院醫生涉嫌當值期間吸食大麻，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">化驗結果卻出乎意料，據了解警方收到醫院第二次尿液測試報告，驗不到醫生體內有大麻成份，他已經獲釋</span></span></span>。 <br />\n<br />\n上月四十八歲姓甄的屯門醫院急症科副顧問醫生，懷疑當值期間吸食大麻，引起各界關注。他最近向警方報到，他已經獲釋。因為警方收到瑪嘉烈醫院進行的第二次尿液測試，驗不到他體內有大麻成份，警方指會再徵詢律政司意見，看看下一步如何做，重案組會繼續調查。 <br />\n<br />\n醫院最初報警，至醫生被警方拘捕，都懷疑他吸食大麻，現在又說沒有，為何會這樣？ 當初憑甚麼懷疑醫生吸食大麻？ <br />\n<br />\n據了解當日醫護人員看見該名醫生精神情緒有異樣，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">醫管局即場跟他抽取尿液樣本，進行快速測試，報告顯示他對大麻成份呈陽性，所以決定報警</span></span>，尿液樣本同時送到瑪嘉烈進行更準確的化驗。 <br />\n<br />\n有藥劑師指有些藥本身雖然沒含大麻，但吃了的話，可能會影響快速測試的試紙出現假陽性，以為身體含大麻素成份。據了解醫院方面知道有關結果，醫生一直放病假，暫時未知何時會上班。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/546344/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E7%96%91%E5%90%B8%E5%A4%A7%E9%BA%BB%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E7%84%A1%E6%A2%9D%E4%BB%B6%E7%8D%B2%E9%87%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F546344%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2590%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E7%258D%25B2%25E9%2587%258B&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUeoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=5124973d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F546344%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2590%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E7%258D%25B2%25E9%2587%258B&h=68333b7b\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/546344/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E7%96%91%E5%90%B8%E5%A4%A7%E9%BA%BB%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E7%84%A1%E6%A2%9D%E4%BB%B6%E7%8D%B2%E9%87%8B</a><br />\n一早講過醫畜係唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,醫死人冇事,就算被metoo法庭都會輕判,不留案底<br />\n醫畜就係有特權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c76c1b309017652d878834545290c7e2c42870","tid":1096071,"uid":108199,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:54:38.000Z","msg":"第二次驗係幾時先<br />\n高薪鐵飯碗果然名不虛傳"},{"pid":"34e6f943cffcfee376240960d94ff9e9a5cee7de","tid":1096071,"uid":11148,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:54:58.000Z","msg":"花咁多資源培訓一個醫畜,點會畀佢有事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f157207756fad2d2e6b2c551616ae892d6d409b8","tid":1096071,"uid":170772,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:56:54.000Z","msg":"大麻全港合法化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f880f1e378c550bb7e3518bd289db2ebf66b07","tid":1096071,"uid":203734,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:57:44.000Z","msg":"食左某d野中和番<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e851b4df8a4f628c9c8a6c86f4e20169cfc444ad","tid":1096071,"uid":6964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd8743d44a24cec02137b1977539623eca6ade8","tid":1096071,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:01:48.000Z","msg":"飲左維他檸檬茶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b33345e0d5bee0e9959d19107cd61c1d4f3e474","tid":1096071,"uid":36494,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"70c76c1b309017652d878834545290c7e2c42870","tid":1096071,"uid":108199,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:54:38.000Z","msg":"第二次驗係幾時先<br />\n高薪鐵飯碗果然名不虛傳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:01:54.000Z","msg":"尿液樣本同時送到瑪嘉烈進行更準確的化驗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同一批尿"},{"pid":"c2ed78b3da08c4dde99f09cff9b0255a05449796","tid":1096071,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:03:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有藥劑師指有些藥本身雖然沒含大麻，但吃了的話，可能會影響快速測試的試紙出現假陽性</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n醫生專業知識救咗自己<br />\n同阿SIR講自己食咗藥, 一場誤會, 係假陽性<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef56c3928fc1af708435d9558d65290f6aec3d54","tid":1096071,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20f880f1e378c550bb7e3518bd289db2ebf66b07","tid":1096071,"uid":203734,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:57:44.000Z","msg":"食左某d野中和番<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:04:33.000Z","msg":"究竟係乜嘢?<br />\n<br />\n醫生真係好勁！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea697330ae61c15ae3caa3add4df688a30ae7e1c","tid":1096071,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:07:16.000Z","msg":"其實最大問題係佢玩失蹤，香港人返工出席好緊要架，有時落街食支煙，買d野飲，遲少少上樓已經俾人篤背脊了"},{"pid":"c951ad4f3849a2e30f6740098ef8d03300c1d9ac","tid":1096071,"uid":3325,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"ef56c3928fc1af708435d9558d65290f6aec3d54","tid":1096071,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20f880f1e378c550bb7e3518bd289db2ebf66b07","tid":1096071,"uid":203734,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:57:44.000Z","msg":"食左某d野中和番<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:04:33.000Z","msg":"究竟係乜嘢?<br />\n<br />\n醫生真係好勁！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:14:33.000Z","msg":"台灣好似有隻野係可以令所有drug test show 陰性<br />\n聽聞 1500 HKD左右"},{"pid":"bf75abc5eca9e32bbaf665aa3b30252ec4800457","tid":1096071,"uid":103156,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:17:07.000Z","msg":"醫生涉食大麻准保釋　<span style=\"color: red;\">屯院拖兩日報警被批醫醫相衞</span><br />\n<br />\n律師黃國桐認為醫管局得知檢驗結果後應及時報警，因為吸食大麻不等於同時藏有大麻，若遲兩天才報警，「有兩日我咩都搬走啦」！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190309/mobile/bkn-20190309094946931-0309_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190309%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190309094946931-0309_00822_001.html&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUeoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=2ba684de\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190309/mobile/bkn-20190309094946931-0309_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ae160ae6a093fd44d1e3ee8385b8771b83a46925","tid":1096071,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef56c3928fc1af708435d9558d65290f6aec3d54","tid":1096071,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20f880f1e378c550bb7e3518bd289db2ebf66b07","tid":1096071,"uid":203734,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:57:44.000Z","msg":"食左某d野中和番<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:04:33.000Z","msg":"究竟係乜嘢?<br />\n<br />\n醫生真係好勁！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:17:54.000Z","msg":"可能食咗幾粒aspirin<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e815463bd595dfbd5f70419cd93b82b2db7563ec","tid":1096071,"uid":35924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea697330ae61c15ae3caa3add4df688a30ae7e1c","tid":1096071,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:07:16.000Z","msg":"其實最大問題係佢玩失蹤，香港人返工出席好緊要架，有時落街食支煙，買d野飲，遲少少上樓已經俾人篤背脊了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:19:45.000Z","msg":"醫生返工咁食無定時，佢話行開食d 野都唔會點啦"},{"pid":"a85acff526421716bdb12c2613cf290a8f6791ad","tid":1096071,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:05:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>藥劑師：兩種西藥可能令尿液大麻測試出現假陽性結果</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1451700_1_L_20190407211744.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1451700_1_L_20190407211744.jpg&h=ab93d9cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方暫時釋放懷疑在當值期間吸食大麻的屯門醫院醫生。消息指，在涉事醫生第一次尿液樣本驗出懷疑大麻成分，但第二次詳細報告卻沒驗出其體內有大麻成份。<br />\n<br />\n香港醫院藥劑師學會會長崔俊明指出，今次的情況罕見，快速測試的準確度已高達95%，但若當事人曾服用非類固醇的消炎止痛藥和抑制胃酸的藥物，都可能會令尿液測試出現假陽性的結果。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，第二次在實驗室的化驗結果會更準確，但樣本成份的濃度和當事人服用的劑量太少等因素，都有機會影響結果，導致無法檢出大麻成份。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，大麻能停留在體內3至5日，服用很重劑量的大麻，大麻成份.有可能會停留在體內7日，在今次的個案事隔已久，再抽尿液樣本化驗亦未必有結果。但他認為，評估有否曾服用大麻，可以了解當事人有否服用會影響結果的兩種西藥，以及事發時的精神狀況等因素。"},{"pid":"2c1178c5e4416fa5ab4273bf79011afd7f3fb94d","tid":1096071,"uid":178365,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"a85acff526421716bdb12c2613cf290a8f6791ad","tid":1096071,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:05:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>藥劑師：兩種西藥可能令尿液大麻測試出現假陽性結果</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1451700_1_L_20190407211744.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.k